{
  "stem": "1550.3",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, our camp was actually in a place called [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Bobasan ?].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Let me say, Mauritius is a beautiful, tropical island with vegetation like you've never seen.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There is green and wild flowers to very steep mountains, and they have green right to the top.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It looks like a tropical paradise.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Absolutely.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "These wild flowers and flowering trees you've never seen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It's absolutely magnificent.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It has become, now, I understand, a big holiday resort.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "People fly there from Paris.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They have regular flights from Paris to Mauritius.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "People fly there, you know?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They have their-- these camps.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But at that time, it didn't exist.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At that time, there was only-- you could only go there by boat.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we arrived at our camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The camp was really not a camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a prison.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What the-- what the British had done, they had cleared the prison of the prisoners, and we were sent to this prison.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now, the prison was organized with two huge cell blocks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Each cell blocks had about 300 or 400 cells-- each individual cells, and a wall around.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there were several other buildings in there, like workshops and storage and so forth.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But they also had built a-- another camp adjacent to it for-- with barracks for about 30-- 30 persons each.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the way it was organized so all the men were in the prison with the cells, while the women were in the adjacent camp.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In other words, each man had a cell to himself, while the women were about 20 or 25 women to one barrack.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that's the way, actually, it stayed for-- for the whole time, for the rest of the period we were in that camp.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, of course.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were never allowed to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
